##--------------------------------------------------------------------
@node Editorial
@title "Editorial"

SWAP & DANCE ISSUE #02 / December 1993.

             Dear Readers,
             +*+*+*+*+*+*+*+

             First, I (SMC) am sorry about the bug
             found in the first issue. It was only
             a simple adress error, but on my A4000
             it don't crashes, coz adress errrors
             don't crash on 68020 +. So I didn't
             recognize the bug.
             This time we have the 2. issue of Swap
             and Dance with lots of new votes and
             text. At this point thanx to all the
             voters.
             Coz of the fact that most of you didn't
             see much of the first issue, we didn't
             remove the old votes, we only added the
             new ones by new voters.

             You can send us following texts:

                @{" Votesheets            " link Votesheets}

                @{" Your own Music Charts " link Owncharts}

                @{" Advertisments         " link Advertisments}

             That's all for know.
             We'll be back in issue #03 early 1994 (Jan!).

             Hope ya like this shit,   SMC

-------------

             Now some words from TOXIC:

             Hey Mates!
             Welcome to the second mindblowing
             issue of the Swap and Dance Charts
             brought to your screen by ABYSS.

             This issue we have a lot of
             improvements for you:

             -It works on all Amigas this time
             (also on lame A 500)
                      ^^^^
             [SMC: NO Amiga is lame ! PC is lame !]


             -New tune by Neurodancer

             -Better Mousepointer

             -All ehrrors fiksed !!!

             So you see, we make all things

             happen just for your pleasure.
             Hope ya can beat that.
             Enjoy reading!

             P.S.:
             Coders out there, whats up
             with joining - write now:

             Toxic of Abyss
             Sven Dedek
             Gruenewaldstr. 6
             84453 Muehldorf
             GERMANY


-------------

               If you have any questions, critics,
               sexual probs or anything else then
               write to :

            THE DUKE            SKINDIVER

            Markus Knauer       Andreas Schwarz
            Fritz-Bender-Str.9  Pfarrer-Ziller-Str15
            85402 Kranzberg     85402 Kranzberg
            Germany             Germany

            TOXIC                 or give our WHQ
                                International Chaos
            Sven Dedek            +1-713-999-3640
            Gruenwaldstr. 6           a call !
            84453 Muehldorf/Inn
            Germany


            either we need some official supporters
            for this little mag. They only have to
            spread the votesheets and get the new
            issue first to spread it too.

            You can send your advertisments (40*20)
            to us, they will be freely shown here.

            Of coz you can send us text about DANCE
            MUSIC, SWAP & MODEM scene news or any-
            thing else.
@endnode
