##--------------------------------------------------------------------
@node Votesheets

            Either you get @{" VOTESHEETS " link Sheets} from one of our
            Swapper or send us a self-printed sheet.


            VOTING RULES:  (We are sure you know!)

            You can't vote for :

                 - YOUR group
                 (For example: If you're Bill Clinton you
                  can't vote for the US Democratic Party!)

                 - ABYSS
                 (the group who made this shit)

                If you vote for one of the above things,
                the vote is invalid and the next Rank (2 or 3)
                moves one place up.


@endnode
