                   PROBS WITH MUNICHS KVR !!!
              ++*+*************************+*++

             Here in munich,bavaria,germany, we've
             lotsa probs with the office respon-
             sible for parties, raves a.s.o. decided
             to do something against drugs on techno
             parties in munich. So they closed all
             raves at 4am (at this time the best
             mood and atmosphere took place).
             Biggest German Rave, the MAYDAY 5 was
             planned in munich, but they (KVR) only
             allowed it till 1am. That was a real
             joke, so MAYDAY take place in Berlin
             on 11.12.93 (The Religion).
             Fact: Munich was on the best way to get
             germanys no.1 rave town, but the office
             (KVR) suxx. Good luck.

